## API Endpoints

### `GET /api/search`
Query parameters:
- `q` - Search query (optional)
- `category` - Filter by category (optional)
- `tags` - Filter by tag substring (optional)
- `hasCard` - Only show skills with cards (optional, boolean)
- `limit` - Max results (default: 50)

Response:
```json
{
  "results": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "angular",
      "category": "architecture",
      "description": "...",
      "tags": ["angular", "v20"],
      "triggers": ["angular", "v20"],
      "score": -2.5,
      "rank": 1,
      "matched_fields": "name,description"
    }
  ]
}
```

### `GET /api/skills/:id`
Returns skill with card data (if exists).

### `PUT /api/skills/:id`
Update skill card. Body:
```json
{
  "use_when": ["..."],
  "avoid_when": ["..."],
  "inputs": "...",
  "outputs": "...",
  "activation": "...",
  "similar": [2, 3],
  "diff_notes": "...",
  "risk_level": "low"
}
```

### `GET /api/metadata`
Returns all categories and tags with counts.

### `POST /api/export`
Body:
```json
{
  "skillIds": [1, 2, 3],
  "format": "markdown" // or "json"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "format": "markdown",
  "content": "# Skill Stack\n\n..."
}
```

