## Security & Safety

- ✅ No authentication required (local-only)
- ✅ No analytics or tracking
- ✅ No external network calls
- ✅ File writes are browser downloads (no server-side writes)
- ✅ SQL injection prevention via prepared statements

## Troubleshooting

### Database not found
Run `npm run init-db` to create the database.

### FTS index out of sync
Run `npm run reindex` to rebuild the FTS index.

### Port 3000 already in use
Change the port: `PORT=3001 npm run dev`

